('rascal-blueprint', 'Rascal Blueprint', 'Fires explosive projectiles that only detonate when hitting ARC.', 'Blueprint', '', 'Legendary', 5000, NULL, 'https://assets.shiesty.me/items/rascal-blueprint.png', 'https://cdn.metaforge.app/arc-raiders/icons/rascal-blueprint.webp', '', '', '', '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '{"range":0,"damage":0,"health":0,"radius":0,"shield":0,"weight":0,"agility":0,"arcStun":0,"healing":0,"stamina":0,"stealth":0,"useTime":0,"duration":0,"fireRate":0,"stability":0,"stackSize":0,"damageMult":0,"raiderStun":0,"weightLimit":0,"augmentSlots":0,"healingSlots":0,"magazineSize":0,"reducedNoise":0,"shieldCharge":0,"backpackSlots":0,"quickUseSlots":0,"damagePerSecond":0,"movementPenalty":0,"safePocketSlots":0,"damageMitigation":0,"healingPerSecond":0,"reducedEquipTime":0,"staminaPerSecond":0,"increasedADSSpeed":0,"increasedFireRate":0,"reducedReloadTime":0,"illuminationRadius":0,"increasedEquipTime":0,"reducedUnequipTime":0,"shieldCompatibility":"","increasedUnequipTime":0,"reducedVerticalRecoil":0,"increasedBulletVelocity":0,"increasedVerticalRecoil":0,"reducedMaxShotDispersion":0,"reducedPerShotDispersion":0,"reducedDurabilityBurnRate":0,"reducedRecoilRecoveryTime":0,"increasedRecoilRecoveryTime":0,"reducedDispersionRecoveryTime":0}'::jsonb, '"<p>The Rascal Blueprint is a rare grenade launcher recipe in ARC Raiders, added in Patch 1.29.0. If you''re wondering how to find the Rascal Blueprint in ARC Raiders - it drops from Raider Containers across all maps and requires a level 2 Gunsmith Workbench to craft.</p><p><strong>Best Ways to Find the Rascal Blueprint:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Raider Containers</strong> — Weapon Cases, Raider Caches, and Ammo Crates are your best source across all maps.</p></li><li><p><strong>Security Breach Lockers</strong> — Breach Lockers scattered across all maps have confirmed drops. Use <a href=\"https://metaforge.app/arc-raiders/map\" target=\"_blank\">Metaforge Interactive Maps</a> to find them.</p></li><li><p><strong>Key Rooms</strong> — Locked rooms with high loot density can also yield the blueprint as a general drop.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Tips to Maximize Rascal Blueprint Drops:</strong> Run Night Raid for boosted rare blueprint drop rates. Safe Pocket the blueprint the moment you find it. Go in naked with <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current\" href=\"https://metaforge.app/arc-raiders/database/item/adrenaline-shot\">Adrenaline Shots</a> to keep farming runs low-risk.</p>"'::jsonb, '{"id":"rascal-blueprint","name":"Rascal Blueprint","description":"Fires explosive projectiles that only detonate when hitting ARC.","item_type":"Blueprint","loadout_slots":[],"icon":"https://cdn.metaforge.app/arc-raiders/icons/rascal-blueprint.webp","rarity":"Legendary","value":5000,"workbench":null,"stat_block":{"range":0,"damage":0,"health":0,"radius":0,"shield":0,"weight":0,"agility":0,"arcStun":0,"healing":0,"stamina":0,"stealth":0,"useTime":0,"duration":0,"fireRate":0,"stability":0,"stackSize":0,"damageMult":0,"raiderStun":0,"weightLimit":0,"augmentSlots":0,"healingSlots":0,"magazineSize":0,"reducedNoise":0,"shieldCharge":0,"backpackSlots":0,"quickUseSlots":0,"damagePerSecond":0,"movementPenalty":0,"safePocketSlots":0,"damageMitigation":0,"healingPerSecond":0,"reducedEquipTime":0,"staminaPerSecond":0,"increasedADSSpeed":0,"increasedFireRate":0,"reducedReloadTime":0,"illuminationRadius":0,"increasedEquipTime":0,"reducedUnequipTime":0,"shieldCompatibility":"","increasedUnequipTime":0,"reducedVerticalRecoil":0,"increasedBulletVelocity":0,"increasedVerticalRecoil":0,"reducedMaxShotDispersion":0,"reducedPerShotDispersion":0,"reducedDurabilityBurnRate":0,"reducedRecoilRecoveryTime":0,"increasedRecoilRecoveryTime":0,"reducedDispersionRecoveryTime":0},"flavor_text":"","subcategory":"","created_at":"2026-05-19T17:19:02.070042+00:00","updated_a